{"tid":1115941,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"［希慎］hot toys 今次真係扮哂嘢","createTime":"2019-04-19T14:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T16:33:50.000Z","uid":63913,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8f6b39c7dd1ec575de99be70b277fa4e835fc3","tid":1115941,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"早兩日去咗佢響希慎廣場搞嘅展覽。事前已經知知要拎籌先入得，點知去到就話四點幾已經派哂。好啦，咁我睇下公仔就算，點知公仔得幾隻，邊好意思話自己係展覽？<br />\n<br />\n最離譜係根本間嘢得小貓三四隻買同睇嘢，根本就唔會迫爆，真係唔明點解要限人數。事實上，多啲人入到場買嘢，對hot toys 嘅營業額都有幫助。佢今次真係多此一舉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來我都覺得hot toys 係香港公司又搞到國際知名，我一直都好支持佢。但今次真係令人好失望。"},{"pid":"2080fd789df5734dede71daabbe1458a4ad0a571","tid":1115941,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"見到有好多人larm入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aecffc4223f9fbe99af015ea034dc0beeece83af","tid":1115941,"uid":73536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aaa828d9cf893b6f94bb6788b1750a85c000fcb4","tid":1115941,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:16:48.000Z","msg":"日日都係三四點就派哂，根本返寫字樓嘅人就一定拎唔到。唔通為咗排隊而攞假咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc89c9cc44e5ab66382a28c789f01f62b10ac140","tid":1115941,"uid":56957,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"佢啲毛公仔cosplay 平時邊有人買<br />\n做到好多搶 好限量咁先有人要"},{"pid":"b12f022be03d192221e4ce367bf41c0415a2a8a4","tid":1115941,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc89c9cc44e5ab66382a28c789f01f62b10ac140","tid":1115941,"uid":56957,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"佢啲毛公仔cosplay 平時邊有人買<br />\n做到好多搶 好限量咁先有人要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:53:17.000Z","msg":"根本大部分貨於全線log on 都搵到，唔明點解要吊高黎賣。"},{"pid":"4eaf3181